How to Use Boil water: Heat water in a kettle or pot until it reaches a rolling boil. Measure tea leaves: Depending on your preference, measure out about 1 teaspoon of Tata Gold Pure and Natural Tea leaves per cup of water. Add tea leaves to a teapot: Place the measured tea leaves into a teapot. Pour hot water: Carefully pour the boiling water over the tea leaves in the teapot. Steep: Allow the tea leaves to steep in the hot water for 3 to 5 minutes, adjusting based on your preferred strength. Strain: Use a strainer to pour the brewed tea into cups, separating the leaves from the liquid. Serve: Enjoy Tata Gold Pure and Natural Tea hot, plain, or with milk, sugar, or lemon as desired. Store remaining tea leaves: After use, reseal the Tata Gold Pure and Natural Tea pack tightly to maintain freshness. product_name: Mtr Badam Drink Mix
product_description: Nutritious almond drink mix with saffron and cardamom
ingredients: Sugar; Milk solids; Almond (8.5%); Maltodextrin; Saffron; Cardamom Antioxidant; Tocopherol
nutritions: Energy (kcal) - 380 Fat (g) - 0.72 Protein (g) - 0.72 Carbohydrates (g) - 12 Of which sugar (g) - 11.4 How to Use Add 3 tsp (15 g) of MTR Badam Drink Mix to 1 cup of hot milk (150 ml). Stir well to ensure the mix blends seamlessly. Serve hot and experience the comforting goodness of badam-infused milk. Refreshing Cold Drink: Experiment with a chilled version of the badam drink. Follow the same instructions but let it cool before serving. Perfect for a refreshing sip on warm days or as an alternative to hot milk. Mix with Oats and Cornflakes: Elevate your breakfast routine by adding MTR Badam Drink Mix to your oats or cornflakes. Enjoy the rich flavour and added nutritional benefits to kickstart your day. Crafted to perfection, this drink mix is a fusion of real badam pieces and authentic saffron, offering a naturally delicious and wholesome choice for your little one. Let's delve into the details of what makes MTR Badam Drink Mix a wellness booster and a delightful treat for your child. The unique blend of badam and Kesar in MTR Badam Drink Mix is crafted to perfection. Real badam pieces and authentic saffron come together to create a drink that not only tantalizes the taste buds but also provides a holistic approach to wellness. Embracing the age-old wisdom that badam and Kesar possess natural qualities beneficial for both the body and mind, MTR Badam Drink Mix is more than just a tasty treat - it's a wellness booster for your child. Purchase; MTR Badam Drink Mix online for your convenience. Relish MTR Badam Drink Mix which is absolutely free from any added chemicals or artificial flavors. Parents can rest assured that their child is enjoying a pure and wholesome beverage without the worry of hidden additives. The commitment to delivering a natural and nutritious drink is reflected in the transparency of the
